  "remarks": "\nMohammed Reza FALLAHZADEH is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: FALLAHZADEH is or has been involved in hostile activity by an armed group backed by the Government of Iran namely threatening, planning or conducting activity which undermines or is intended to undermine the integrity, prosperity or security of the United Kingdom or any other country. \n",
